data: {"index":2,"blockType":"tool_use","finalContent":"{\"id\": \"INC-20260221-0001\", \"note\": \"Initial diagnostics complete. Findings: (1) Prometheus: 54 targets scraped, 3 DOWN in agentic-dev (code-manager, openagentic-synth, kubernetes-apiservers). (2) Kubernetes MCP: kubeconfig initialization failed - cannot list pods. (3) Loki: 200 errors in 15min - 174 ERROR-level, dominated by PostgreSQL FK constraint violations on user_query_audit table. Also found Milvus embedding dimension mismatches and varchar overflow errors.\", \"action_type\": \"FINDING\"}","toolId":"toolu_bdrk_012bnoMbHuonzDCqU1kd1w9W","toolName":"incident_add_note"}

