data: {"messageId":"TfReJw-KaGT0ashRjyqDc","role":"assistant","content":"## Incident Created & Diagnostics Complete\n\n**Incident ID:** `INC-20260221-0001`\n**Title:** VAL-04 Test: API Latency Spike\n**Severity:** SEV2 | **Status:** INVESTIGATING\n**Service:** openagentic-api\n**Created:** 2026-02-21T00:31:34.975Z\n\n---\n\n## Diagnostic Results\n\n### 1. Prometheus Service Availability (`up` query)\n\n**54 targets** scraped. **51 UP, 3 DOWN** (94.4% availability).\n\n| Target | Instance | Status | Namespace |\n|--------|----------|:------:|-----------|\n| **openagentic-api** | `10.42.5.20:8000` | ✅ UP | agentic-dev |\n| **openagentic-mcp-proxy** | `10.42.5.25:8080` | ✅ UP | agentic-dev |\n| **openagentic-crewai** | `10.42.1.90:3200` | ✅ UP | agentic-dev |\n| **openagentic-langgraph** | `10.42.1.91:3100` | ✅ UP | agentic-dev |\n| **openagentic-code-manager** | `10.42.5.19:8080` | ❌ DOWN | agentic-dev |\n| **openagentic-openagentic-synth** | `10.42.2.37:8090` | ❌ DOWN | agentic-dev |\n| **kubernetes-apiservers** | `10.2.10.131:6443` | ❌ DOWN | default |\n\n### 2. Kubernetes Pod Health (agentic-dev)\n\n⚠️ **Kubernetes MCP kubeconfig initialization failed** — `Invalid kube-config file. No configuration found.` This is a **known issue** from previous audits. Pod listing could not be completed via the Kubernetes MCP. Prometheus data above provides partial visibility.\n\n### 3. Loki Error Search (agentic-dev, last 15m)\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|------:|\n| **Total errors found** | **200** |\n| **ERROR-level entries** | 174 |\n| **FAILED-level entries** | 26 |\n\n#### Error Breakdown by Source\n\n| Source Pod | Error Type | Severity |\n|------------|-----------|:--------:|\n| **openagentic-postgresql-0** | FK constraint violation: `user_query_audit_message_id_fkey` — INSERT on `user_query_audit` fails because parent `message` record doesn't exist | ❌ Critical |\n| **openagentic-milvus-standalone** | `result_summary` varchar exceeds 512 char limit (520 chars) in `tool_success_tracking` collection | ⚠️ Warning |\n| **openagentic-milvus-standalone** | Embedding dimension mismatch: float data length 1024 vs expected dim 1536 in `chat_conversations_v2` | ⚠️ Warning |\n| **openagentic-milvus-standalone** | `field source not exist` in `azure_sdk_documentation` search | ⚠️ Warning |\n| **openagentic-milvus-standalone** | Collections `chat_conversations` and `app_documentation` not found | ⚠️ Warning |\n| **openagentic-mcp-proxy** | Admin MCP returning HTTP 500 (3 occurrences) | ⚠️ Warning |\n| **openagentic-api** | Tool execution batch failures (3 failed calls at 00:29:29, 2 at 00:29:34) | ⚠️ Warning |\n\n---\n\n## Key Findings\n\n> [!WARNING]\n> **Primary contributor to latency:** The PostgreSQL FK constraint violations on `user_query_audit` are occurring on every tool call, creating cascading retry/failure cycles. This is the **same issue** identified in the previous incident `INC-20260220-0001`.\n\n**1. PostgreSQL Audit Race Condition (P0)**\n- **Pattern:** `INSERT INTO user_query_audit` fires before the parent `message` record commits\n- **Rate:** ~174 errors in 15 minutes (~11.6/min)\n- **Impact:** Audit trail is silently broken; each failed INSERT adds latency to the request path\n\n**2. Two OpenAgentic Pods DOWN (P1)**\n- **code-manager** (`10.42.5.19:8080`) and **openagentic-synth** (`10.42.2.37:8090`) are unreachable\n- **Impact:** Code execution and OAT workflows are offline\n\n**3. Milvus Schema Mismatches (P2)**\n- Embedding dimension mismatch (1024 vs 1536) blocking conversation memory writes\n- VARCHAR overflow in `tool_success_tracking` collection\n- Missing collections and fields suggesting schema drift","timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:32:17.602Z","mcpCalls":[{"id":"toolu_bdrk_01YQ1Pt1wVRtk7LF474Jf7ze","name":"incident_create","tool":"incident_create","toolName":"incident_create","serverId":"openagentic_incident","serverName":"openagentic_incident","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"title":"VAL-04 Test: API Latency Spike","description":"Automated test - elevated p99 latency detected","severity":"sev2","service":"openagentic-api"},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Incident Created ===\n\n🟠 SEV2 | 📋 OPEN\nID: INC-20260221-0001\nTitle: VAL-04 Test: API Latency Spike\nService: openagentic-api\nCreated: 2026-02-21T00:31:34.975257Z\n\nNext steps:\n  1. Assign the incident: incident_assign(id, assignee)\n  2. Update status to investigating: incident_update_status(id, 'investigating')\n  3. Add updates as you investigate: incident_add_note(id, note)"}],"structuredContent":{"result":"=== Incident Created ===\n\n🟠 SEV2 | 📋 OPEN\nID: INC-20260221-0001\nTitle: VAL-04 Test: API Latency Spike\nService: openagentic-api\nCreated: 2026-02-21T00:31:34.975257Z\n\nNext steps:\n  1. Assign the incident: incident_assign(id, assignee)\n  2. Update status to investigating: incident_update_status(id, 'investigating')\n  3. Add updates as you investigate: incident_add_note(id, note)"},"isError":false},"status":"completed","startTime":1771633894808,"endTime":1771633897313,"duration":2505,"timestamp":"2026-02-21T00:31:37.313Z"},{"id":"toolu_bdrk_01SsZXjHACJs4ZWBvXjGxE89","name":"prometheus_query","tool":"prometheus_query","toolName":"prometheus_query","serverId":"openagentic_prometheus","serverName":"openagentic_prometheus","executedOn":"mcp-proxy","arguments":{"query":"up"},"result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Query: up\nResult Type: vector\nResults: 54\n\n  {\"__name__\": \"up\", \"openagentic_io_docker_builds\": \"enabled\", \"openagentic_io_runner_type\": \"builder\", \"beta_kubernetes_io_arch\": \"amd64\", \"beta_kubernetes_io_instance_type\": \"k3s\", \"beta_kubernetes_io_os\": \"linux\", \"feature_node_kubernetes_io_cpu_cpuid_ADX\": \"true\", \"feature_node_kubernetes_io_cpu_cpuid_AESNI\": \"true\", \"feature_node_kubernetes_io_cpu_cpuid_AVX\": \"true\", \"feature_node_kubernetes_io_cpu_cpuid_AVX2\": \"true\", \"feature_node_kubernetes_io_cpu_cpuid_CMPXCHG8\": \"true\", \"feature_